{
  "texts": [
    "• We have not automatically linked the factory data CSV file loading process to the chatbot app.",
    "The process is still done manually, and we will consider upgrading this task to automatic loading in future versions of the chatbot app.",
    "Manuscript highlights• System downtime is costly to factories.• We design a generative AI chatbot HMI as a tool to alleviate system downtime.",
    "• We customize and integrate the current GPT 3.5 LM functions in our system back-end.",
    "• We obtain a responsive chatbot HMI extracting queried information from trained data."
  ]
}